What you need to know:

European Super League, Andrea Agnelli, Juventus, Andrea Pirlo, Massimiliano Allegri, Cristiano Ronaldo, Champions LeagueJuventus were knocked out of Italy's top four last weekend following a 3-0 home defeat by AC Milan, leaving coach Andrea Pirlo's position increasingly under threat entering the final three gamesJuventus last missed out on the Champions League in 2011 while Cristiano Ronaldo, the competition's all-time leading scorer with 134 goals, has featured in every edition since 2003